        "Importance of natural resources",
        "Uses of natural resources"
      ],
      "teaching_strategy": [
        "Textbook reading",
        "Teacher explanation with real-life examples"
      ],
      "student_activities": [
        "List natural resources found in the local environment",
        "Discuss how they are used"
      ],
      "assessment": ["Short written answers", "Class participation"]
    },
    {
      "period": 4,
      "title": "Renewable and Non-Renewable Resources",
      "topics_covered": [
        "Definition of renewable resources",
        "Definition of non-renewable resources",
        "Examples and differences"
      ],
      "teaching_strategy": [
        "Comparison table explanation",
        "Interactive questioning"
      ],
      "student_activities": [
        "Write examples of renewable and non-renewable resources",
        "Discuss why conservation is important"
      ],
      "assessment": ["Notebook activity", "Short concept explanation"]
    },
    {
